        <li><strong>Aadhaar OTPs go to mom's phone</strong> — she's the legal owner so she's the one signing. Son drives the keyboard but mom has the final say on every submission.</li>
        <li><strong>Use Aadhaar e-KYC paths everywhere.</strong> GST + FSSAI + Trademark all offer Aadhaar-OTP verification that skips physical visits. Saves ~5 days per registration.</li>
