        <li><strong>WhatsApp Business autoresponder</strong> — "Mom replies during the day; orders ship Tue + Sat." Sets clear expectations.</li>
        <li><strong>Batch all shipping for Wed evening + Sat afternoon.</strong> Two packing sessions per week handles ~30–50 orders/month.</li>
        <li><strong>Mom's home = pickup point + manufacturing premises.</strong> No second address to manage. Shiprocket courier picks up at her door.</li>
        <li><strong>Don't bother with offline retail for the first 6 months.</strong> D2C + Amazon (once State License lands) is enough. Retail visits eat weekends.</li>
        <li><strong>Use Shiprocket Plus (₹999/month) once mom crosses 100 orders/month.</strong> Gets her 5% off all shipments + priority support — saves more than it costs.</li>
